Sorry that this has sat for so long. We have been thinking about how to handle ExtensionDtypes generally. It should be enough to add handling of `pd.DatetimeTZDtype` to the [_dtypes file](https://github.com/dask/dask/blob/main/dask/dataframe/_dtypes.py). Something like:

```python
    @make_array_nonempty.register(pd.DatetimeTZDtype)
